did.abstract: Serial issues, pamphlets, leaflets, newsletters, bulletins, and election campaign material relating to libertarianism, issued by the Libertarian Party and other libertarian organizations in the United States, including many state, local, and campus libertarian groups, and by libertarian organizations in Canada.

accessrestrict.head: Access
accessrestrict.p: The Hoover Institution Archives only allows access to copies of audiovisual items. To listen to sound recordings or to view videos or films during your visit, please contact the Archives at least two working days before your arrival. We will then advise you of the accessibility of the material you wish to see or hear. Please note that not all audiovisual material is immediately accessible.

userestrict.head: Publication Rights
userestrict.p: For copyright status, please contact the Hoover Institution Archives.

prefercite.head: Preferred Citation
prefercite.p: [Identification of item], David Walter collection, [Box number], Hoover Institution Archives.

acqinfo.head: Acquisition Information
acqinfo.p: Acquired by the Hoover Institution Archives in 1992.

accruals.head: Accruals
accruals.p: Materials may have been added to the collection since this finding aid was prepared. To determine if this has occurred, find the collection in Stanford University's online catalog at http://searchworks.stanford.edu/. Materials have been added to the collection if the number of boxes listed in the online catalog is larger than the number of boxes listed in this finding aid.

scopecontent.head: Scope and Content of Collection
scopecontent.p: This collection consists of serial issues, bulletins, pamphlets, newsletters, campaign material, and newspapers circulated and created by the Libertarian Party of the United States, the Libertarian Party of Canada, and various other libertarian organizations, including those headquartered in states and in local communities, and student run groups on various college campuses. These materials were collected by David Walter, an editor of several publications and active member of the Libertarian Party and Society for Individual Liberty.

scopecontent.head: Scope and Contents note
scopecontent.p: Posters, stickers, photographs, and other material relating to David Walter and his activities in the Libertarian Party.

scopecontent.head: Scope and Contents note
scopecontent.p: Publications created specifically by state libertarian parties in the United States. Includes serial issues and information on national conventions.

scopecontent.head: Scope and Contents note
scopecontent.p: Serial issues of nationally and internationally distributed libertarian publications.
